%% Diagram: Cqrs Separates Write Command And Read Query Paths Events Synchronize Them Asynch
%% Type: flowchart
flowchart LR
    subgraph Commands
        C[Command] --> WM[Write Model]
        WM --> DB[(Primary DB)]
        WM --> E[Events]
    end

    subgraph Queries
        E --> RM[Read Model Builder]
        RM --> RDB[(Read DB)]
        Q[Query] --> RDB
    end

    style DB fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
    style RDB fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#6c8ebf
